{"tid":2492896,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔當ViuTV係友台？歐陽震華指只停留係80年代亞視","createTime":"2021-04-17T12:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T14:51:23.000Z","uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ab39406eda780273bab3125ae410bef352c670","tid":2492896,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"藝人歐陽震華（Bobby）與馬德鐘（Joe）今日為新劇《伙記辦大事》宣傳，現場還有十多架鐵騎造勢。講到新劇口碑不俗，Bobby稱是大家功勞，問到是否預期之內？他說：「唔係，之後仲會上。」又開玩笑指現時有40點收視，預計之後有70點收視，發揮搞笑本色。<br />\n<br />\n想互換角色<br />\n<br />\n講到友台ViuTV來勢洶洶，他反問：「仲有咩友台？我仲停留喺80年代嘅ATV。（你係收視福將唔擔心？）唔好畀啲無形枷鎖我，都係要睇表現，好似馬德鐘依家係視帝，佢都努力咗好多年。（對收視有信心？）套套都會問收視，觀眾睇得開心最重要。」他指最初是有意飾演Joe亦正亦邪的角色：「監製話你都係做<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUpypARDoHAsDV8NxKr1AYy6HNh93sdN2GM6XJFdqKUQo?filename=b3iV6YR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3iV6YR.jpg&h=0b51ceaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正派，你做反派好多人會笑。」Joe也想交換角色：「有乜理由唔係我做G4。」現實中曾做過G4的他，直言入行以來從未飾演過G4角色。<br />\n<br />\n唔覺同陳瀅係忘年戀<br />\n<br />\n劇中Joe與年紀相差21年的陳瀅飾演情侶，被指忘年戀，Joe說：「我冇諗呢樣嘢，我覺得OK，我哋唔係後生仔女嗰種激烈，而係細水長流。」Bobby就自言跟萬綺雯在劇中關係未有明確交代，形容是閨蜜，又指現實中多閨蜜：「晚晚打畀我，全部都係唔開心先搵我，我好似聆聽者咁畀意見。（唔怕太太呷醋？）我啲閨蜜太太全部都識，高矮肥瘦古靈精怪乜都有，所以太太好放心。」<br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLwgLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=06f4d8b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>"},{"pid":"29dca2e68588d303eaf56ab1b833827cbb9c3ff8","tid":2492896,"uid":33709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"咁咪搵返啲80年代睇你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339b859440c4f03d401acdc2fc6218689177375e","tid":2492896,"uid":73586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"行過街邊見到歐陽震華個廣告<br />\n<br />\n成個咸濕阿叔咁<br />\n柒到不得了"},{"pid":"d2d0cf419b51fbd408323feca14fbbd2da1ed6ac","tid":2492896,"uid":95520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"又開玩笑指現時有40點收視，預計之後有70點收視，發揮搞笑本色。<br />\n<br />\n而家呢個年代搞笑真係容易"},{"pid":"01dd8c84421f81621c64b68b36f8e7a4d2ba4eed","tid":2492896,"uid":13653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:55:01.000Z","msg":"馬德鐘同陳浩民非禮完人又出返黎拍劇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416f3fe1fe35b6dcd2c49159a2ded0702b394a77","tid":2492896,"uid":210669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"小學嗰陣睇啲劇已經係佢地兩個做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過左咁多年仲係佢地"},{"pid":"b4b5157ea6e4f5012e83d443caa84c4e952d11d3","tid":2492896,"uid":193693,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:14:22.000Z","msg":"完全唔知佢又拍劇<br />\n仲要播緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係返去睇ViuTV lu"},{"pid":"2b58da9d52acd95de945a6605021dafbb35075ab","tid":2492896,"uid":218082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"TVB呢班藍屍死賤種啲節目冇人睇係咁借viutv刷存在感,借完姜濤抽水又係咁借啲意串鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲閪節目留返老人院啲老嘢睇啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76adc4313d48cff3699954e7720aee2295a40598","tid":2492896,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"原來TVB停留咗喺80年代亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0cf8a1d3838e4fd79ce3d04d92f35f516bf786","tid":2492896,"uid":16818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"喂啊tvb班垃圾唔好咁好肉酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b080bbc3257e689edabaec2de31aa1c2e94f06","tid":2492896,"uid":67657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14: